============================================================
EXERCISE 15 - ticketraisingapp | HOL 15: React Forms
============================================================
Category  : Mandatory
Topic     : Controlled components, form inputs, handleSubmit
App Name  : ticketraisingapp
Status    : COMPLETED ✅

------------------------------------------------------------
FORM CONTROLS USED
------------------------------------------------------------
  <input type="text" />  → Employee Name (textbox)
  <textarea />           → Complaint description
  <button type="submit"> → Submit Complaint (handleSubmit)

  Controlled Components:
  value={empName}     onChange={this.handleChange}
  value={complaint}   onChange={this.handleChange}

------------------------------------------------------------
EXECUTION FLOW
------------------------------------------------------------
  1. User types name → handleChange() → setState({ empName })
  2. User types complaint → setState({ complaint })
  3. User clicks "Submit Complaint"
     → handleSubmit(e) called
     → e.preventDefault() → no page reload
     → Reference number generated: TKT-XXXXXX
     → alert() shows: "Complaint Registered! Ref: TKT-847291"
     → Form resets to empty

